{"tw": {"3443640": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "偵探荒鹿：詛咒的驅魔師", "steam_appid": 3443640, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/extras/172fcedd5b021cfda502306714c5d71a.avif?t=1767833671\" width=616 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你在醫院醒來，卻失去了所有記憶。他們告訴你，你是犬蔡村山體滑坡的倖存者之一，口袋裡僅有一些零錢。沒有人知道你的身份，但你顯然與這個村莊有所關聯。為了尋找真相，你前往事發地點，希望能喚醒哪怕一點記憶。然而，你發現村莊竟然完好無損，村民的生活彷彿一切如常。更可怕的是——你無法離開，而這個村莊，似乎隱藏著某種詭異的秘密…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/extras/c4dd28e7799f3f8fa0451f1b0fbc8a14.avif?t=1767833671\" width=616 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在這款視覺小說中，你將扮演悠木，與驅魔師協會派遣的伊早瀨荒鹿一同調查這座本應被掩埋的詭異村莊。偽裝成偵探，審問村民，並協助其他同樣被困在村莊中的倖存者。你的選擇將改變故事的發展，決定你的結局——成功生還，還是墮入深淵？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/extras/ba9943505aaf585248ea5cda953d2eb6.avif?t=1767833671\" width=616 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/extras/47e17a47e0b9e53e7fb41f415f0b667f.avif?t=1767833671\" width=616 height=503 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/extras/a023538269a5110b2ebd6f3cc893a072.avif?t=1767833671\" width=616 height=503 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/extras/35c9c1004c89ae980ffa85043f7badd4.avif?t=1767833671\" width=616 height=503 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/extras/8b3e8258f00bf4af22938ea077898690.avif?t=1767833671\" width=616 height=503 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/extras/83f0b48172beac212be8881b0add4c2f.avif?t=1767833671\" width=616 height=160 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>選擇決定命運</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在旅途中，你將面臨各種抉擇。有些選擇或許能拯救生命，而有些則可能讓你提前迎來死亡……務必謹慎行動！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多重結局</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲擁有不止一種結局，而且並非所有結局都是美滿的。你能解鎖所有結局嗎？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>引人入勝的世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >曲折離奇的劇情、豐富的世界觀、扣人心弦的對話，以及等待解開的重重謎團，將讓你沉浸在這個奇妙的故事之中。</p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/extras/172fcedd5b021cfda502306714c5d71a.avif?t=1767833671\" width=616 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你在醫院醒來，卻失去了所有記憶。他們告訴你，你是犬蔡村山體滑坡的倖存者之一，口袋裡僅有一些零錢。沒有人知道你的身份，但你顯然與這個村莊有所關聯。為了尋找真相，你前往事發地點，希望能喚醒哪怕一點記憶。然而，你發現村莊竟然完好無損，村民的生活彷彿一切如常。更可怕的是——你無法離開，而這個村莊，似乎隱藏著某種詭異的秘密…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/extras/c4dd28e7799f3f8fa0451f1b0fbc8a14.avif?t=1767833671\" width=616 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在這款視覺小說中，你將扮演悠木，與驅魔師協會派遣的伊早瀨荒鹿一同調查這座本應被掩埋的詭異村莊。偽裝成偵探，審問村民，並協助其他同樣被困在村莊中的倖存者。你的選擇將改變故事的發展，決定你的結局——成功生還，還是墮入深淵？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/extras/ba9943505aaf585248ea5cda953d2eb6.avif?t=1767833671\" width=616 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/extras/47e17a47e0b9e53e7fb41f415f0b667f.avif?t=1767833671\" width=616 height=503 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/extras/a023538269a5110b2ebd6f3cc893a072.avif?t=1767833671\" width=616 height=503 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/extras/35c9c1004c89ae980ffa85043f7badd4.avif?t=1767833671\" width=616 height=503 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/extras/8b3e8258f00bf4af22938ea077898690.avif?t=1767833671\" width=616 height=503 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/extras/83f0b48172beac212be8881b0add4c2f.avif?t=1767833671\" width=616 height=160 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>選擇決定命運</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在旅途中，你將面臨各種抉擇。有些選擇或許能拯救生命，而有些則可能讓你提前迎來死亡……務必謹慎行動！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多重結局</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲擁有不止一種結局，而且並非所有結局都是美滿的。你能解鎖所有結局嗎？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>引人入勝的世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >曲折離奇的劇情、豐富的世界觀、扣人心弦的對話，以及等待解開的重重謎團，將讓你沉浸在這個奇妙的故事之中。</p>", "short_description": "在這款扣人心弦的視覺小說中，你將扮演失憶少年悠木，與頂級驅魔師伊早瀨荒鹿攜手合作，一同揭開犬蔡村的黑暗秘密，拼湊出失落的記憶。", "supported_languages": "英文, 日文<strong>*</strong>, 簡體中文, 繁體中文<br><strong>*</strong>具備完整音效支援的語言", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/9a54e4a8eb13da1bee826e2f8b64cb0c5a7f5146/header_tchinese.jpg?t=1767833671", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/20d23b2861ee26a7b741879487bc84633970068f/capsule_231x87_tchinese.jpg?t=1767833671", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/20d23b2861ee26a7b741879487bc84633970068f/capsule_184x69_tchinese.jpg?t=1767833671", "website": "https://saikeystudios.com", "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows® 7/8/8.1/10<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core2 Duo or better<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> DirectX 9/OpenGL 4.1 capable GPU<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 2 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "legal_notice": "2025 Saikey Studios", "developers": ["Kenshisuki Square"], "publishers": ["Saikey Studios"], "price_overview": {"currency": "TWD", "initial": 22600, "final": 22600, "discount_percent": 0, "initial_formatted": "", "final_formatted": "NT$ 226"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "單人"}, {"id": 62, "description": "親友同享"}], "genres": [{"id": "25", "description": "冒險"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2025 年 10 月 17 日"}}}}, "us": {"3443640": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Detective Araka", "steam_appid": 3443640, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/extras/15f42835384336fb45f7c40d51f84451.avif?t=1767833671\" width=616 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You wake up in the hospital with no memories. They tell you that you were found among the survivors of a landslide that buried a small village called Inusai, with only some spare change in your pocket. Nobody knows who you are or where you came from, but you are undoubtedly connected to the village in some way. Determined to uncover what happened to you, you set off to investigate the site, hoping that something will trigger at least some fleeting memory. Everything becomes even more complicated when you discover the village is still completely intact and its residents are behaving as if nothing happened. Very soon, however, you realize you can no longer leave, and that nothing is as it seems.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/extras/4cf3b4f0c6d270232516f974f800f8ad.avif?t=1767833671\" width=616 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this visual novel, take on the role of Yuuki and work alongside Ihayase Araka, sent by The Exorcist Association to investigate the eerie village that should have been buried beneath the landslide. Disguised as a detective, interrogate villagers and assist other survivors who are stuck in the village just like you. Make choices along the way that will shape your path and determine your success—or your demise.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/extras/7e13c1d68a7c2e3c7f4d5e3364cbe6fe.avif?t=1767833671\" width=616 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/extras/bc7eaf4810ab49022043cc8c1ffee5b1.avif?t=1767833671\" width=616 height=503 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/extras/664ca869772abe17d6033f968bc83965.avif?t=1767833671\" width=616 height=503 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/extras/dd2b9505de432f8a1735ad2327934132.avif?t=1767833671\" width=616 height=503 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/extras/1f88bda9f5e3f52979fdce187f8fe331.avif?t=1767833671\" width=616 height=503 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/extras/3d968564229694e0c8a0d5f245985c96.avif?t=1767833671\" width=616 height=160 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Choices Matter</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will face decisions along the way that will shape your journey.  Some choices might save a life, or might even lead to your early demise, so tread carefully!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Multiple Endings</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is more than one ending, and not all of them end in a happily ever after.  Can you uncover them all?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A World to Get Drawn Into</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game boasts a winding story story filled with rich lore, engaging dialogue, and mysteries to uncover.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/extras/15f42835384336fb45f7c40d51f84451.avif?t=1767833671\" width=616 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You wake up in the hospital with no memories. They tell you that you were found among the survivors of a landslide that buried a small village called Inusai, with only some spare change in your pocket. Nobody knows who you are or where you came from, but you are undoubtedly connected to the village in some way. Determined to uncover what happened to you, you set off to investigate the site, hoping that something will trigger at least some fleeting memory. Everything becomes even more complicated when you discover the village is still completely intact and its residents are behaving as if nothing happened. Very soon, however, you realize you can no longer leave, and that nothing is as it seems.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/extras/4cf3b4f0c6d270232516f974f800f8ad.avif?t=1767833671\" width=616 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this visual novel, take on the role of Yuuki and work alongside Ihayase Araka, sent by The Exorcist Association to investigate the eerie village that should have been buried beneath the landslide. Disguised as a detective, interrogate villagers and assist other survivors who are stuck in the village just like you. Make choices along the way that will shape your path and determine your success—or your demise.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/extras/7e13c1d68a7c2e3c7f4d5e3364cbe6fe.avif?t=1767833671\" width=616 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/extras/bc7eaf4810ab49022043cc8c1ffee5b1.avif?t=1767833671\" width=616 height=503 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/extras/664ca869772abe17d6033f968bc83965.avif?t=1767833671\" width=616 height=503 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/extras/dd2b9505de432f8a1735ad2327934132.avif?t=1767833671\" width=616 height=503 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/extras/1f88bda9f5e3f52979fdce187f8fe331.avif?t=1767833671\" width=616 height=503 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/extras/3d968564229694e0c8a0d5f245985c96.avif?t=1767833671\" width=616 height=160 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Choices Matter</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will face decisions along the way that will shape your journey.  Some choices might save a life, or might even lead to your early demise, so tread carefully!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Multiple Endings</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is more than one ending, and not all of them end in a happily ever after.  Can you uncover them all?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A World to Get Drawn Into</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game boasts a winding story story filled with rich lore, engaging dialogue, and mysteries to uncover.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "short_description": "In this gripping visual novel, step into the shoes of Yuuki, a boy with amnesia, and team up with top-tier exorcist Ihayase Araka. Together, you must uncover the dark secrets of Inusai Village and piece together your forgotten past.", "supported_languages": "English, Japanese<strong>*</strong>, Simplified Chinese, Traditional Chinese<br><strong>*</strong>languages with full audio support", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/header.jpg?t=1767833671", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/a6d647e85f454afae686255c400fbce15d9422b6/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1767833671", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3443640/a6d647e85f454afae686255c400fbce15d9422b6/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1767833671", "website": "https://saikeystudios.com", "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS *:</strong> Windows® 7/8/8.1/10<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel Core2 Duo or better<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 4 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> DirectX 9/OpenGL 4.1 capable GPU<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 2 GB available space</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "legal_notice": "2025 Saikey Studios", "developers": ["Kenshisuki Square"], "publishers": ["Saikey Studios"], "price_overview": {"currency": "USD", "initial": 1199, "final": 1199, "discount_percent": 0, "initial_formatted": "", "final_formatted": "$11.99"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "Single-player"}, {"id": 62, "description": "Family Sharing"}], "genres": [{"id": "25", "description": "Adventure"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "Oct 17, 2025"}}}}, "fetched_at": "2026-04-23T07:42:13Z"}